{"tid":175184,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔係串] 真心想知渣自動波車D人擺手係波棍做咩","createTime":"2017-03-27T10:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T11:35:40.000Z","uid":37107,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b223746dd536a60b399a71fc253ad0e2a9dc9be","tid":175184,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:26:35.000Z","msg":"一考到牌就買棍 真係未試過渣自動波<br />\n<br />\n自動波係咪可以行車途中都要換波?<br />\n<br />\n唔係既話有時見佢地明明唔就手都要擺上去係做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb45b596ae9526b7954675698e3da28b468c08d","tid":175184,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"自動波起步/行緊都要轉波<br />\n係唔洗踩離合"},{"pid":"2f63b04352aa48927ae7153cd91000c817ed8a4b","tid":175184,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:34:09.000Z","msg":"自動波好似都有咩D同1,2之分，1,2呢兩個波段就好似我地啲低波咁，但基本D都行得哂。<br />\n不過自動波感覺好似會容易揸得定同省油。<br />\n講樂趣一定係棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f361e627be4255c9847e953571e3f64d511c98cd","tid":175184,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自動波起步/行緊都要轉波<br />\n係唔洗踩離合</blockquote><br />\n姐係都要1&gt;2&gt;3&gt;4&gt;5&gt;6咁轉? 未渣過真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我見佢隻手唔洗郁.. 個波棍又咁撚高 真係就手&quot;long&quot;住咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DyoxK4iz32I?t=108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDyoxK4iz32I%3Ft%3D108&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=96333d42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DyoxK4iz32I?t=108</a>"},{"pid":"f23874c81b283532babf69b536301b1c1f2a9f44","tid":175184,"uid":9670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一考到牌就買棍 真係未試過渣自動波<br />\n<br />\n自動波係咪可以行車途中都要換波?<br />\