/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無喇喇又關撥片檔咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊輔助加減波wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca438dee34dea679a8e3baff89cc11b65465b1b","tid":175184,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有加減波架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咩年代渣車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇車唔好扮有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n棍同撥片都做到加減，只係我唔鍾意用撥片咪用番棍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無喇喇又關撥片檔咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊輔助加減波wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你貼你部車睇下係咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b544bb53ad9f7d0921950efb72ecd72de6df709d","tid":175184,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有加減波架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咩年代渣車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇車唔好扮有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n棍同撥片都做到加減，只係我唔鍾意用撥片咪用番棍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無喇喇又關撥片檔咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊輔助加減波wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係話唔用撥片 用支棍做加減囉 點極都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63424d9b54ca6333647404a03aab1605950714e","tid":175184,"uid":61693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"揸錢七,方便有時急剎拖波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46c40f8907d41022856e004870964c0a36a491f","tid":175184,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有加減波架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咩年代渣車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n仲有好多車加減波都用棍</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有咩車無棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://iamhk.org/pages/加減波心法.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiamhk.org%2Fpages%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%9B%E6%B3%A2%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95.html&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8514c705\" target=\"_blank\">http://iamhk.org/pages/加減波心法.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係全自動 全自動加輔助加減<br />\n手動 定 手動加輔助加減<br />\n其實成日講棍波代表手動入波<br />\n咁唔通自動波果支唔叫棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇埋個網都完全唔明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之，仲有好多自動波車既加減波功能係用支棍黎控制，唔一定係撥片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b15793b26883dd72d0f574a575e3348144b4e54","tid":175184,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落s 波用😂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> S波cut的士佬"},{"pid":"017527e7458a8e261a1ff7b7fb9ba97a6109b0f6","tid":175184,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有加減波架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咩年代渣車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n仲有好多車加減波都用棍</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有咩車無棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://iamhk.org/pages/加減波心法.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiamhk.org%2Fpages%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%9B%E6%B3%A2%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95.html&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8514c705\" target=\"_blank\">http://iamhk.org/pages/加減波心法.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係全自動 全自動加輔助加減<br />\n手動 定 手動加輔助加減<br />\n其實成日講棍波代表手動入波<br />\n咁唔通自動波果支唔叫棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇埋個網都完全唔明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之，仲有好多自動波車既加減波功能係用支棍黎控制，唔一定係撥片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自動波支棍有+/-或者S波B波咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定可能佢淨係揸法拉利 未揸過其他車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c14d8b16ee3020eac5840a4a1ebe008bae99a88","tid":175184,"uid":67719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有加減波架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咩年代渣車？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n仲有好多車加減波都用棍</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n有咩車無棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://iamhk.org/pages/加減波心法.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiamhk.org%2Fpages%2F%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%9B%E6%B3%A2%E5%BF%83%E6%B3%95.html&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8514c705\" target=\"_blank\">http://iamhk.org/pages/加減波心法.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係全自動 全自動加輔助加減<br />\n手動 定 手動加輔助加減<br />\n其實成日講棍波代表手動入波<br />\n咁唔通自動波果支唔叫棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇埋個網都完全唔明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之，仲有好多自動波車既加減波功能係用支棍黎控制，唔一定係撥片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自動波支棍有+/-或者S波B波咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定可能佢淨係揸法拉利 未揸過其他車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如大家睇下上面有條友問咩先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我夠知加減可以用棍檔可以有撥片檔<br />\n鬼唔知媽是女人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面有條友 ：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自動波都有加減波既咩</span></strong></span><br />\n重有 一樣野撥片波最初只係賽車級既車先有<br />\n一般車系係唔流行<br />\n係近呢十幾年先連一般車都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4